ea095575" style="height:380px;width:675px;" alt="TMA" data-uuid="4cf40065-e424-3c03-bca1-79a1eb2e8e71"><figcaption></figcaption> <div class="photo-credit">Square Enix公司</div></figure></a><p><em>《最终幻想 XVI》</em>在 PlayStation 5 上独占的时间不会太长。 Square Enix 已确认 PC 移植版正在正式开发中。考虑到该游戏 2020 年的第一个预告片提到了 PC 版本，这并不算太令人震惊，但是嘿，确认一下就好了。</p><p>制作人吉田直树表示，开发团队已经开始制作两部分“付费 DLC”。希望它会有更多的叙事内容，而不仅仅是更棘手的老板和挑战。</p><p><strong>继续阅读。</strong></p><p></p><h2> <a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/spotify-reportedly-locks-white-noise-podcasters-out-of-an-ad-program-150124532.html">Spotify 可能会将白噪音播客排除在其广告计划之外</a></h2><h3>目的可能是提高公司的利润。</h3><h3></h3><p>据<em>彭博社</em>报道，从 10 月 1 日起，白噪音播客将不再有资格参加 Spotify 的大使广告计划。根据该计划，Spotify 向播客付费，让其阅读该公司自有产品的广告。其目标是让更多人为该平台制作节目。</p><p><em>彭博社</em>此前报道称，一些白噪音播客每月的收入高达 18,000 美元，这在很大程度上要归功于 Spotify 向他们支付广告投放费用。报告称，大使广告在白人平静播客上效果不佳，因为听众通常不像对话或叙事播客那样投入。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/spotify-reportedly-locks-white-noise-podcasters-out-of-an-ad-program-150124532.html"><strong>继续阅读。</strong></a></p><p></p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><h2> <a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-logitech-g-pro-x-superlight-2-improves-an-already-great-gaming-mouse-070133238.html">罗技 G Pro X Superlight 2 改进了本来就很出色的游戏鼠标</a></h2><h3>USB-C 充电和全机械开关。</h3> <a href="https://www.engadget.com/the-logitech-g-pro-x-superlight-2-improves-an-already-great-gaming-mouse-070133238.html"><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/0f15b500-4bc7-11ee-bc3f-9b7a6a55b506" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/0f15b500-4bc7-11ee-bc3f-9b7a6a55b506" style="height:405px;width:675px;" alt="TMA" data-uuid="eb81235a-215e-34fb-9fb7-7fff5e9342f8"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">恩杰特</div></figure></a><p>罗技 (Logitech) 的 G Pro X Superlight 是最受欢迎的游戏鼠标之一，该公司只是让它变得更好。 G Pro X Superlight 2 的电池续航时间现在为每次充电 95 小时，而其前身为 70 小时。当快速抬起或倾斜鼠标时，新的 Hero 2 传感器可提供更稳定的跟踪。它还将最大每英寸点数 (DPI) 提高到 32,000，跟踪速度提高到每秒 500 英寸 (IPS)。罗技还已将按钮转向全机械开关，并且现在支持 USB-C 充电。最后。即日起发售，售价 159 美元。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-logitech-g-pro-x-superlight-2-improves-an-already-great-gaming-mouse-070133238.html"><strong>继续阅读。</strong></a></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-bmws-high-efficiency-concept-ev-111559673.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-bmws-high-efficiency-concept-ev-111559673.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> f69bea93-454a-4f74-8bcc-fbf1b6c783a9</guid><dc:creator>马特·史密斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 05 Sep 2023 11:15:59 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693903264</ingested><modified> 2023-09-05T08:41:10+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mat Smith]]></category><media:content height="2638" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/04958d00-4b2f-11ee-a0df-5532ed758b48" width="4000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2638" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/04958d00-4b2f-11ee-a0df-5532ed758b48" width="4000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[BMW]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[A white BMW is on a gravel path with steps on one side and grass on the other.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[BMW 'Vision Neue Klasse' concept]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The Logitech G Pro X Superlight 2 improves an already great gaming mouse]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>自<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/logitech-g-pro-x-superlight-151239203.html">2020 年推出</a>以来， <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/logitech-g-pro-x-superlight-mouse-irl-140037783.html">罗技 G Pro X Superlight</a>一直是最受爱好者和电子竞技专业人士<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://prosettings.net/guides/gaming-mouse/">欢迎的</a>游戏鼠标之一，今天罗技通过一些关键更新对其进行了更新。 <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5sb2dpdGVjaGcuY29tL2VuLXVzL3Byb2R1Y3RzL2dhbWluZy1taWNlL3Byby14Mi1zdXBlcmxpZ2h0LXdpcmVsZXNzLW1vdXNlLjkxMC0wMDY2MjguaHRtbCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMjAzOGM4YjEtMDFjYy00MGQ3LWJiZWEtOTgwNDk3YTNjYjJlIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAc-cnO22bJWRJSgMcs1vRZRgc6Nf4ctnRD0eAqLuWv1Q&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.logitechg.com%2Fen-us%2Fproducts%2Fgaming-mice%2Fpro-x2-superlight-wireless-mouse.910-006628.html" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.logitechg.com/en-us/products/gaming-mice/pro-x2-superlight-wireless-mouse.910-006628.html">罗技 G Pro X Superlight 2</a> （新的无线型号）与其前身具有相同的宜人形状，但消除了该设备的许多小烦恼。即日起即可订购，价格为 159 美元。</p><p>首先，G Pro X Superlight 2 通过 USB-C 充电和连接，而之前的型号则使用古老的 microUSB 端口。新鼠标没有使用全机械开关（随着时间的推移可能会导致意外双击问题），而是采用了罗技<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5sb2dpdGVjaGcuY29tL2VuLXVzL3Byb2R1Y3RzL2dhbWluZy1taWNlL2c1MDIteC13aXJlZC1saWdodGZvcmNlLjkxMC0wMDYxNDQuaHRtbCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMjAzOGM4YjEtMDFjYy00MGQ3LWJiZWEtOTgwNDk3YTNjYjJlIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAetaHkvt1q6K2RoMKnz41IrYgCDpqGtImqH5BsH9H6RL&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.logitechg.com%2Fen-us%2Fproducts%2Fgaming-mice%2Fg502-x-wired-lightforce.910-006144.html" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.logitechg.com/en-us/products/gaming-mice/g502-x-wired-lightforce.910-006144.html">G502 X 系列</a>中的“ <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5sb2dpdGVjaGcuY29tL2VuLXVzL2lubm92YXRpb24vbGlnaHRmb3JjZS5odG1sIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIyMDM4YzhiMS0wMWNjLTQwZDctYmJlYS05ODA0OTdhM2NiMmUifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAcJxwznHX9f6PgKIZrFSvc3rqJ-rIZzAvMOSWM1ibtCV&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.logitechg.com%2Fen-us%2Finnovation%2Flightforce.html" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.logitechg.com/en-us/innovation/lightforce.html">Lightforce</a> ”开关。这是一种包含机械和光学部件的混合解决方案，其想法是平衡前者的感觉与后者更快的速度和（通常）更高的耐用性。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>除此之外，电池续航时间现在从每次充电 70 小时延长至 95 小时。据称，新的“Hero 2”传感器在快速举起或倾斜鼠标时可提供更稳定的跟踪。 （它还将最大 DPI 和跟踪速度分别提高到 32,000 和 500 IPS，尽管这两个数字对大多数人来说都有点过分了。）最大轮询率从 1,000Hz 跃升至 2,000Hz – 一些游戏鼠标可以<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/razer-viper-8k-181937540.html">高达 8,000 Hz</a> ，但这几乎没有什么实际好处，除非您使用刷新率特别高的显示器。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/af0e78c0-480d-11ee-b17f-dd7b06278540" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/af0e78c0-480d-11ee-b17f-dd7b06278540" style="height:1200px;width:2000px;" alt="罗技 G Pro X Superlight 2 无线游戏鼠标的侧面。仅左侧有两个可自定义按钮。" data-uuid="13c8cebc-b2c1-35c9-8004-3dab97fdedb4"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">摄影：Jeff Dunn / Engadget</div></figure><p>我已经拥有 G Pro X Superlight 2 几天了。就像第一个 Superlight 一样，这里的主要吸引力是双手灵巧的“土豆”式形状，它应该适合几乎任何手部尺寸或<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://switchandclick.com/mouse-grips/">握把类型</a>。这仍然是一种“万事通，无能”的情况：例如， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Razer;elmt:;cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=d043077a-4ba1-4321-a933-30b8701d8d31&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Razer&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiJkMDQzMDc3YS00YmExLTQzMjEtYTkzMy0zMGI4NzAxZDhkMzEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cucmF6ZXIuY29tL2dhbWluZy1taWNlL3JhemVyLWRlYXRoYWRkZXItdjMtcHJvIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIyMDM4YzhiMS0wMWNjLTQwZDctYmJlYS05ODA0OTdhM2NiMmUifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAVJehgJ9RC4r0_LJL_1QfpC2EaELxcHXT4VNYhSr5Sx-&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.razer.com%2Fgaming-mice%2Frazer-deathadder-v3-pro" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.razer.com/gaming-mice/razer-deathadder-v3-pro">Razer DeathAdder V3 Pro</a>的轮廓更适合较大的手和手掌握把。但这种设计对于更广泛的人群来说是安全的。</p><p> G Pro X Superlight 2 重 60 克，仅比其前身轻约 3 克。如今，许多选择在技术上都比较轻，但没有一个认真的人可以称其为重。外壳依然坚固，没有“蜂窝”式的<a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/razer-viper-mini-signature-edition-ultra-light-gaming-mouse-174510979.html">孔洞</a>，而且与第一代Superlight相比，塑料上的纹理感觉更高级一些。</p><p>不出所料，我的性能问题也为零。在<em>《光环：无限》</em>等多人射击游戏、 <em>《博德之门 3》</em>等慢节奏角色扮演游戏以及日常工作中，跟踪一直准确且一致，而点击记录没有明显的延迟。 PTFE（又名聚四氟乙烯）脚比以前稍长和稍宽，但无论哪种方式滑动都很顺畅。 （背面 USB 接收器隔室可选用 PTFE 盖，可增加一点额外的速度。）滚轮不能向左或向右倾斜，但相对安静、抓地力强且精确。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/0a579cc0-480e-11ee-9fff-4ecae69f9a21" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/0a579cc0-480e-11ee-9fff-4ecae69f9a21" style="height:1200px;width:2000px;" alt="罗技 G Pro X Superlight 2（左）看起来与原来的 G Pro X Superlight（右）几乎相同，但它确实进行了一些有意义的改进。" data-uuid="f789b79d-2ba5-3716-ba04-b7644d41b0b4"><figcaption> G Pro X Superlight 2（左）的外观与原来的 Superlight（右）几乎相同。</figcaption><div class="photo-credit">摄影：Jeff Dunn / Engadget</div></figure><p>与此同时，新的光学机械开关为每次按下提供了独特的触感。它们听起来比第一个 Superlight 更低音，但感觉更紧。 DeathAdder V3 Pro 上的全光学开关——目前是我的<a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-gaming-mouse-140004638.html">游戏鼠标购买指南</a>中的首选——相比之下显得更加模糊。罗技不会提供主要按钮可以承受多少次点击的具体估计，但理论上，这种混合设计应该比传统的机械开关更耐用。如果这是一个问题，您可以通过罗技的 G Hub 软件打开“仅光学”模式，但这会缩短电池寿命。</p><p>一些妥协得以延续。没有 RGB 灯光、没有蓝牙、也没有专用的 DPI 切换按钮。左侧有两个可自定义的快捷按钮，但右侧没有，因此鼠标并不是真正灵巧的。罗技的 G Hub 软件使分配宏和 DPI 配置文件变得相当容易，包括单独定制水平和垂直运动灵敏度的能力，但很多人过去发现它有问题。而这一切都不便宜。如果你拥有原来的 Superlight，那么这里可能没有足够的新品来证明你再花 159 美元是值得的。</p><p>也就是说，考虑到这款鼠标专门针对有竞争意识的玩家，其中一些遗漏是可以预料到的。我必须验证罗技的电池寿命声明，但如果你愿意花钱购买高性能鼠标，但没有明确的人体工程学形状，G Pro X Superlight 2 看起来是最佳选择。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/41deb340-480e-11ee-9ff9-51116615363a" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/41deb340-480e-11ee-9ff9-51116615363a" style="height:1200px;width:2000px;" alt="罗技 G Pro X TKL 无线游戏键盘。" data-uuid="fcdbf238-aba0-348f-9fb8-4eaff3d6505b"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">摄影：Jeff Dunn / Engadget</div></figure><p>除了新款鼠标之外，罗技还推出了新款无线游戏键盘<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5sb2dpdGVjaGcuY29tL2VuLXVzL3Byb2R1Y3RzL2dhbWluZy1rZXlib2FyZHMvcHJvLXgtdGtsLXdpcmVsZXNzLWtleWJvYXJkLmh0bWwiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjIwMzhjOGIxLTAxY2MtNDBkNy1iYmVhLTk4MDQ5N2EzY2IyZSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAcNjAzvWpHgI-YXM7EYRy07nq18uqqAsply5eL1kPl3D&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.logitechg.com%2Fen-us%2Fproducts%2Fgaming-keyboards%2Fpro-x-tkl-wireless-keyboard.html" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.logitechg.com/en-us/products/gaming-keyboards/pro-x-tkl-wireless-keyboard.html">G Pro X TKL</a> 。该无钥匙型号现已上市，售价 199 美元。在这里，您可以看到双镜头 PBT 键帽、每键 RGB 背光、专用媒体键、坚固的金属底座以及通过 G Hub 进行的常用软件定制套件。除了无线适配器之外，它还可以通过蓝牙和可拆卸的 USB-C 电缆进行连接，并且<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5sb2dpdGVjaGcuY29tL2VuLXVzL2lubm92YXRpb24vbWVjaGFuaWNhbC1zd2l0Y2hlcy5odG1sIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIyMDM4YzhiMS0wMWNjLTQwZDctYmJlYS05ODA0OTdhM2NiMmUifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAYyCQrOITAJdgLGVKgCXhCkk1HhBOAf9zvkFC21JhapX&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.logitechg.com%2Fen-us%2Finnovation%2Fmechanical-switches.html" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.logitechg.com/en-us/innovation/mechanical-switches.html">可使用</a>罗技的触觉（GX 棕色）、线性（GX 红色）或点击式（GX 蓝色）开关。罗技表示您可以更换第三方键帽，并且电池续航时间为 50 小时。</p><p>在很多方面，G Pro X TKL 都让人想起<a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/logitech-g915-tkl-keyboard-hands-on-150013237.html?guccounter=1&amp;guce_referrer=aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZ29vZ2xlLmNvbS8&amp;guce_referrer_sig=AQAAAIYjMKSykK3YBwXn-WnvU2VwjFhFpgGXVYsEh2ZRcE4ckUQY63zlTQ8eyxyuT56rCgAqZ4_lUJoQK11DS20WM7bSfHPZfpED7rOoMsAbs4X2G3OmWs4WHCo67LooNZmQdevtoVDD3D7vT_XfiqLFKTTUuLf9A4Y9xiwo1qURJm_D">罗技的 G915 TKL</a> ，只不过它使用传统的机械开关而不是低调的开关。使用几天后，感觉<em>还不错</em>：按键清脆、间隔良好且没有明显的松动声，可定制的 RGB 看起来很锐利，罗技的无线技术也很可靠。它还配有一个实用的手提箱。但我的设备上的 GX Brown 开关声音相当大，并且缺乏其他高端游戏主板（例如<a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1" href="https://wooting.io/wooting-60he">Wooting 60HE</a>或<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:SteelSeries;elmt:;cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=e8351d9d-883b-4d2b-9ca2-def694c65fa7&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=SteelSeries&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAUfD_T0We079mtnKcxG6Y94TFsyAbCUiO3pV6mAhUGjz&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fsteelseries.com%2Fgaming-keyboards%2Fapex-pro-tkl-wireless-2023" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://steelseries.com/gaming-keyboards/apex-pro-tkl-wireless-2023">SteelSeries Apex Pro TKL）</a>的一些高级功能。没有<a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-05-28-steelseries-apex-pro-custom-key-travel.html">可调节驱动</a>、<a data-i13n="cpos:18;pos:1" href="https://wooting.io/rapid-trigger">快速触发</a>或<a data-i13n="cpos:19;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-10-01-logitech-mechanical-keyboard-switches.html">热插拔开关</a>。对于 199 美元的价格，有些人可能会发现缺乏功能集。但如果您需要 TKL 外形的无线机械键盘，这里的产品至少感觉舒适且做工精良。 </p><p><core-commerce id="da6473d66f1b40409672477741c08ce1" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p><core-commerce id="02663e9ff66b46daaae1528559258d25" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/the-logitech-g-pro-x-superlight-2-improves-an-already-great-gaming-mouse-070133238.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-logitech-g-pro-x-superlight-2-improves-an-already-great-gaming-mouse-070133238.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 2038c8b1-01cc-40d7-bbea-980497a3cb2e</guid><dc:creator>杰夫·邓恩</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 05 Sep 2023 07:01:33 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693926582</ingested><modified> 2023-09-05T15:10:00+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Information Technology]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Hobbies & Personal Activities]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jeff Dunn]]></category><media:content height="1200" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/8da2de60-480d-11ee-95fe-7d750fc2445b" width="2000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1200" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/8da2de60-480d-11ee-95fe-7d750fc2445b" width="2000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Photo by Jeff Dunn / Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[The new Logitech G Pro X Superlight 2 wireless gaming mouse.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Logitech G Pro X Superlight 2]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Nintendo's new mobile game lets you pluck Pikmin on your browser]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>任天堂与 Niantic 合作推出了一款新的《皮克敏》手机游戏，这款游戏主要适合打发时间，而不是严肃的游戏。它被称为<em>“Pikmin Finder”</em> ，正如<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.nintendolife.com/news/2023/09/nintendo-launches-mobile-browser-game-pikmin-finder"><em>《Nintendo Life》</em></a>指出的那样，两家公司在西雅图举行的 Nintendo Live 活动上及时发布了它。您可以通过手机上的任何浏览器访问增强现实游戏，无论是 iPhone 还是 Android 设备。我们已经在多种浏览器上进行了尝试，包括 Chrome 和 Opera，只要您允许它访问您的相机，我们就可以验证它是否有效。</p><p>与<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/niantic-pikmin-bloom-rollout-052408547.html"><em>《Pikmin Bloom》</em></a>类似，该游戏将皮克敏叠加在您通过手机摄像头看到的环境中。然后你可以通过向上滑动来捕捉这些生物——请注意，当你发现一个生物时，周围通常潜伏着更多相同颜色的生物。之后，您可以使用您拨出的皮克敏来寻找宝藏，包括蛋糕和橡皮鸭。您甚至会在屏幕上看到他们给您带来这些宝藏。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/b2bb57d0-4bb5-11ee-bbfb-309e11cce1b0" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/b2bb57d0-4bb5-11ee-bbfb-309e11cce1b0" style="height:800px;width:480px;" alt="红色皮克敏叠加在键盘上。" data-uuid="48d303c2-88d4-3656-b522-531923042348"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">皮克敏探测器</div></figure><p>要玩游戏，您可以通过移动浏览器访问其<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://pikmin-finder.nintendo.net/">网站</a>，然后开始在手机上捕捉皮克敏。您还可以扫描在桌面浏览器上打开网站时显示的二维码。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/nintendos-new-mobile-game-lets-you-pluck-pikmin-on-your-browser-064423362.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/nintendos-new-mobile-game-lets-you-pluck-pikmin-on-your-browser-064423362.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> ce7445db-6d28-444a-8b98-b1d51cdc7302</guid><dc:creator>玛丽埃拉·穆恩</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 05 Sep 2023 06:44:23 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693896245</ingested><modified> 2023-09-05T06:44:09+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Utility Industry]]></category><category><![CDATA[Personal Finance - Career & Education]]></category><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Handheld & Connected Devices]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mariella Moon]]></category><media:content height="720" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/83803990-4bb0-11ee-bf6d-199b1c5976db" width="1280"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="720" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/83803990-4bb0-11ee-bf6d-199b1c5976db" width="1280"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Business Wire]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA["Pikmin Short Movies" Pikmin are a mysterious mix of plant and animal. Captain Olimar is an astronaut who happens to come to their planet. Pikmin live together with him and collect various treasures on the planet. Pikmin come out from their game world and appear in a CG animation film. This omnibus film contains three short episodes: "The Night Juicer," in which Captain Olimar makes his favorite juice; "Treasures in a Bottle," in which Pikmin meet a strange treasure; "Occupational Hazards," a big adventure at a construction site. (C)Nintendo]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[27th Tokyo International Film Festival Welcomes "Father of Super Mario" Shigeru Miyamoto (Nintendo Game Producer) to Screen "PIKMIN Short Movies"]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Vampire: The Masquerade - Bloodlines 2 returns from the shadows with a new developer]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>两年前，Paradox Interactive 与该游戏的前开发商 Hardsuit Labs 分道扬镳，并<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/vampire-the-masquerade-bloodlines-2-indefinite-delay-165029556.html"><ins>无限期推迟了该游戏</ins></a>，两年后<em>，《吸血鬼：避世血统 2》</em>已从开发地狱的深渊中崛起。出版商此后招募了<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-08-08-dear-esther-ios-release.html"><em><ins>《亲爱的埃丝特》</ins></em></a> <em>&nbsp;</em> <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2015-04-16-everybodys-gone-to-the-rapture-trailer-song.html"><em><ins>每个人都沉浸在狂喜</ins></em></a>之中<em>&nbsp;</em> The Chinese Room 工作室正在开发 2004 年原版 RPG 的续作<em>。《血族 2》</em>预计将于 2024 年秋季推出。</p><p> Chinese Room 保留了一些原始概念，同时抛弃了其他概念，以自己的愿景重新构建<em>《血统 2》</em> 。现代西雅图的场景以及 Hardsuit 的一些关卡和艺术设计都得以保留。然而，创意总监 Alex Skidmore 告诉<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.pcgamer.com/vampire-the-masquerade-bloodlines-2-has-been-quietly-rebuilt-by-dear-esther-developer-the-chinese-room-with-different-gameplay-mechanics-and-rpg-systems/"><em><ins>PC Gamer</ins></em></a> ，该游戏现在拥有“一个具有不同游戏机制和 RPG 系统的新代码库。”你将扮演一个年长的吸血鬼，而不是你<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2014-11-24-ccp-games-kills-a-fan-remake-of-vampire-the-masquerade-bloodl.html"><ins>在原版游戏中</ins></a>可能熟悉的新鲜面孔。虽然主角已经停滞了一段时间，所以你会和他们同时适应寒冷的环境。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><div id="6f61d3d840d24f438f93917cfbcb205b"><div style="left:0;width:100%;height:0;position:relative;padding-bottom:56.25%;"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/2clSTM3UvTo?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></div><p>对于 The Chinese Room 来说，这是一种新的挑战，到目前为止，The Chinese Room 一直专注于充满神秘感的大气步行模拟器，正如<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.polygon.com/23858293/perhaps-vampire-the-masquerade-bloodlines-2-release-date-developer-the-chinese-room"><em><ins>Polygon</ins></em></a>所言<em>&nbsp;</em>笔记。 <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/vampire-the-masquerade-bloodlines-2-delayed-2021-200243795.html"><ins>就像它的最新项目一样，</ins></a>该工作室多年来也经历了自己的麻烦。 2017 年，由于资金问题，该公司<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2017-09-24-everybodys-gone-to-the-rapture-creator-goes-dark.html"><ins>几乎完全关闭，</ins></a>随后 Sumo Digital 接手并重振了它（Sumo Digital 本身后来<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tencent-sumo-acquisition-091425058.html"><ins>找到了新的所有者，即腾讯</ins></a>）。</p><p>在接下来的几个月里，我们将进一步了解 The Chinese Room 为粉丝们准备的内容。 Paradox 计划在一月份更深入地讨论<em>《吸血鬼：避世血统 2》</em> 。 </p><div id="946bc5f1956341c7813e01154950499b"><div style="left:0;width:100%;height:0;position:relative;padding-bottom:56.25%;"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/D6b6LGubq6I?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></div><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/vampire-the-masquerade---bloodlines-2-returns-from-the-shadows-with-a-new-developer-200008403.html?src =rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/vampire-the-